15:40.130 --> 15:44.250
我会尽我所能帮你抓住那个狗娘养的
I'll do whatever I can to help you nail that son of a bitch.

15:44.260 --> 15:46.090
你认为录音带在莎拉那里?
You think Sara has this tape?

15:46.100 --> 15:49.690
不  政府这样认为
Government does.

15:49.700 --> 15:51.350
我昨天还见过她
I just saw her yesterday.

15:51.360 --> 15:53.790
她自己都不知道她有那东西
If she does have anything, she doesn't know.

15:53.800 --> 15:55.690
她现在在哪儿?
Well, where is she now?

15:55.700 --> 15:57.190
