I don't know.

15:57.200 --> 15:59.150
有什么办法可以联系到她?
Any way you can get in touch with her?

15:59.160 --> 16:01.750
买个手机  我打电话给他
We brought cell phones.I could call her.

16:01.760 --> 16:03.790
拜托  拜托  老兄
Please, please, please, bro,

16:03.800 --> 16:05.520
到巴拿马再打电话给她
call her from Panama.

16:05.530 --> 16:07.350
我们只有不到两个小时了
We got less than two hours.

16:07.360 --> 16:10.630
我要赶上飞机
I got to make the flight.

16:12.530 --> 16:16.800
什么?
What?

16:18.300 --> 16:19.620
快跑
Run!

16:19.630 --> 16:23.130
快跑!
Run!

16:27.130 --> 16:29.190
你刚才说的那辆车在哪儿?
where's this car you keep talking about?

16:29.200 --> 16:30.550
就在山后面
- It's over the ridge.

16:30.560 --> 16:31.520
把枪给我
- Give me that.

16:31.530 --> 16:34.490
你们去开车!
You guys head for the car!

16:34.500 --> 16:37.800
快!
Go!

16:52.360 --> 16:54.400
快!  走!
Come on! Go!

16:54.660 --> 16:58.130
回去接他!
Go back for him!

17:01.560 --> 17:05.360
爸!
Dad!

17:09.330 --> 17:12.700
走!
Go!

17:14.460 --> 17:17.350
成功了!  狗娘养的!
Son of a bitch! We made it!

17:17.360 --> 17:20.930
成功了!
We made it!

17:23.500 --> 17:27.100
林肯
Linc.

17:39.480 --> 17:42.470
苏克雷  带我们去医院
Sucre, get us to a hospital.

17:42.480 --> 17:44.300
这儿? 见鬼  我还要去找...
Out here? Where the hell am I going to find...?

17:44.310 --> 17:46.040
带我们去医院  求你!
Just get us to a hospital, please!

17:46.050 --> 17:47.770
好吧
Okay.

17:47.780 --> 17:49.540
别担心  你会没事的
Don't worry. You're going to make it.

17:49.550 --> 17:52.270
这是胆汁  他把我打穿了
It's bile. He got me clean through.

17:52.280 --> 17:56.300
你会没事的...坚持住
You're going to be okay! Just... hold on.

17:56.310 --> 17:59.970
你们两个  听我说
Listen to me, both of you.

17:59.980 --> 18:02.140
对不起
I'm sorry.

18:02.150 --> 18:05.470
我希望我从未离开过你们
I wish I had never left.

18:05.480 --> 18:11.250
别说话  别说话  呼吸
Don't talk, don't talk. Just breathe.

18:15.110 --> 18:18.370
好了  你想要一个香蕉花生酱三明治吗?
Okay, so do you want a pb & b?

18:18.380 --> 18:19.940
不要
Not really.

18:19.950 --> 18:23.600
我肚子痛
My tummy hurts.

18:23.610 --> 18:25.240
她的背包呢?
Where's her knapsack?

18:25.250 --> 18:27.240
她的什么?
Her what?

18:27.250 --> 18:30.000
她的背包  她的药在里面
Knapsack. Her medicine's in it.

18:30.010 --> 18:32.000
我不知道  我刚才抱起她就跑
I don't know, baby. I just grabbed her and ran.

18:32.010 --> 18:33.940
她需要吃药
She needs that medicine.

18:33.950 --> 18:35.000
两天不吃就不行
She can't go two days without it.

18:35.010 --> 18:36.570
是的  我知道
Yeah, I know.

18:36.580 --> 18:37.740
我是她爸爸  好吗?
I'm her father, all right?

18:37.750 --> 18:40.170
在哪儿?
Where is it?

18:40.180 --> 18:42.400
宝贝  冷静点  你在找什么?
Baby.Baby, look. Calm down.What are you looking for?

18:42.410 --> 18:45.070
告诉我是什么  我能帮你找  好吗?
Just tell me what it is, and I'll go ahead and get it, okay?

18:45.080 --> 18:47.840
她的处方
Her prescription.

18:47.850 --> 18:50.170
是个备份
It's a backup.

18:50.180 --> 18:51.770
保险起见我另外保留了一个
I keep an extra, in case.

18:51.780 --> 18:52.740
好的
Okay.

18:52.750 --> 18:55.200
好的
Okay.

18:55.210 --> 19:01.850
我们只要去药店买就行
so all we need to do is find a pharmacy.

19:02.850 --> 19:05.970
别担心
Don't worry.

19:05.980 --> 19:08.870
嘿   看起来我们要去兜一圈 小宝贝
Hey, looks like we're going on a ride, sweet pea.

19:08.880 --> 19:12.700
我们绑住了帝博格 他可能拿了加里的东西
Look, we nail Bagwell, he might still have some of Geary's things on him,

19:12.710 --> 19:15.200
比如背包  他有些私人物品在里面
like his backpack,which has his personal stuff in it.

19:15.210 --> 19:17.740
他妻子喜欢的东西
I know his wife would love to have it.

19:17.750 --> 19:20.170
如果我们找到博格威尔 你可以私下交给她
If we find Bagwell, you can give it to her personally.

19:20.180 --> 19:21.800
-谢谢 -这也是我仅仅能做的
Thanks. -It's the least I can do considering ho you're helping me out.

19:21.810 --> 19:26.570
因为你帮了我很多 虽然有人还在担心...
Though some of the guys on the force are concerned about...

19:26.580 --> 19:28.500
他们担心什么?
what are they concerned about?

19:28.510 --> 19:32.170
没什么 只是你知道
Nothing.But you know what?

19:32.180 --> 19:33.700
为什么你没有告诉我所有的事情?
Why don't you tell me what you know, we'll get Geary's effects back to his family,

19:33.710 --> 19:35.400
我们能抓住博格威尔  拿回加里的家庭财产
we'll track down Bagwell,

19:35.410 --> 19:39.700
我敢肯定所有人与此有关的人都会知道 你对我们的帮助十分宝贵
I'll make sure that everybody involved knows that your help was invaluable.

19:39.710 --> 19:41.770
我还是劝你说出大部分
I'll even recommend that you get most of,

19:41.780 --> 19:43.840
那笔悬赏金
if not all of, that reward money.

19:43.850 --> 19:45.840
那到底
What is it exactly

19:45.850 --> 19:50.370
警方的人在怀疑些什么?
that the guys
on the force were concerned about?

19:50.380 --> 19:53.570
他们有人认为 你头上的伤还有疑点
Well, some of them thought that you weren't being totally upfront about your head injury.

19:53.580 --> 19:56.940
我是说  实际上这的确有点反常
I mean, to be fair, it does seem a little off

19:56.950 --> 20:01.850
你会没看见从前面 袭击你正脑门儿的人
that you didn't see the guy who hit you smack-dab on the forehead.

20:03.880 --> 20:06.540
你厉害
You got me.

20:06.550 --> 20:08.840
盖瑞和我
Geary and me

20:08.850 --> 20:12.300
对于怎么去找到博格威尔起了点分歧
had a little dustup over how to go about finding Bagwell.

20:12.310 --> 20:14.770
然后我们动起手来  他打了我
It got physical, and he hit me.

20:14.780 --> 20:17.240
我们俩打架就好象兄弟间那种
The two of us, we fought like brothers.

20:17.250 --> 20:21.200
我不想到警察面前去告他一状
I didn't want to rat him out to the cops.

20:21.210 --> 20:25.000
打完后  我们分开了
After the fight, we split up.

20:25.010 --> 20:28.200
之后...
And then...

20:28.210 --> 20:32.500
你知道之后他发生了什么...
Well, you know what happened to him.

20:32.510 --> 20:35.100
我真希望当初我们没打架  你明白吗?
I just wish to hell we'd never fought, you know?

20:35.110 --> 20:37.800
也许他现在就还活着...
Maybe then he'd still be...

20:37.810 --> 20:42.880
布拉德  你不能这么责怪自己
Brad, you can't blame yourself.

20:44.650 --> 20:46.300
我们为什么不将悲痛化为力量
Why don't we refocus our energy on

20:46.310 --> 20:51.050
来找那个杀了你朋友的人?
finding the man who killed your friend?

20:51.980 --> 20:57.410
罗伊也一定这么想
That's what Roy would've wanted.

21:13.250 --> 21:17.040
好了吧  宝贝儿
All right, baby.

21:17.050 --> 21:19.000
有保险吗?
Insurance card?

21:19.010 --> 21:21.270
没  我没有保险
Uh, no, I don't have insurance.

21:21.280 --> 21:24.300
你开消炎药不用保险?
You're paying for dexamethasone without insurance?

21:24.310 --> 21:25.970
有医疗补贴补助什么的吗?
You got medicaid, medicare or something?

21:25.980 --> 21:28.770
没有
Nope.

21:28.780 --> 21:30.140
我用现金付就好了
Um, I'll just pay cash.

21:30.150 --> 21:34.750
一共125块
It's $125.

21:37.850 --> 21:41.850
(仍然在逃的罪犯及家人)

21:43.550 --> 21:45.470
请问?
Excuse me?

21:45.480 --> 21:49.370
好了吗?
Excuse me?

21:49.380 --> 21:54.150
哦  对不起
Um, oh, sorry.

22:01.780 --> 22:05.400
很抱歉我没零钱了
Sorry I don't have anything smaller.

22:05.410 --> 22:09.200
我到后面去把这100块换开
I have to go to the back to get change for $100.

22:09.210 --> 22:13.280
马上就回来
So... I'll be right back.

22:23.910 --> 22:24.840
就在那儿! 医院!
- Right there! Hospital!

22:24.850 --> 22:26.070
我看见了  我看见了
- I see it. I see it.

22:26.080 --> 22:27.070
快带我们过去
Just get us there.

22:27.080 --> 22:28.300
不  你们会被抓的
No, you'll be caught.

22:28.310 --> 22:30.900
那就被抓吧
Then we'll be caught.

22:30.910 --> 22:32.470
我不会让你死的
I'm not gonna let you die.

22:32.480 --> 22:34.640
那就听我的
Then listen to me.

22:34.650 --> 22:37.940
去找莎拉 唐克雷蒂
You find Sara Tancredi.

22:37.950 --> 22:41.740
她能终结这一切
She can end this.

22:41.750 --> 22:46.010
都看你的了
It's up to you now.

22:54.380 --> 22:57.440
通缉一辆深蓝色小轿车
yeah, I want an alarm out on a dark blue Sedan.

22:57.450 --> 22:59.770
车牌AE9268.
License: AE9268.

22:59.780 --> 23:02.100
洛斯克鲁斯东南40英里处
40 miles southeast of Los Cruces.

23:02.110 --> 23:04.700
现在就去办
Do it now.

23:06.880 --> 23:08.270
该死的!
oh, come on!

23:10.280 --> 23:12.510
什么事?
What?

23:13.500 --> 23:14.500
哪家医院?
What hospital?

23:24.010 --> 23:26.570
医生就报警了 就在里面
Docs called us in,He's in here.

23:27.880 --> 23:29.540
我们查了他的名字
We ran his name.

23:29.550 --> 23:34.770
结果查到他正受到两项走私毒品的通缉
Came back with two federal drug smuggling warrants out on him.

23:34.780 --> 23:38.150
听说你想和我谈谈
Heard you wanted to talk to me.

23:39.750 --> 23:42.600
我有些你们感兴趣的信息...
I got some information the feds want...

23:42.610 --> 23:47.980
有关迈克尔 斯科菲尔德的
about Michael Scofield.

23:49.580 --> 23:51.840
比如他会在哪儿搭飞机
Like where he's catching a ride.

23:51.850 --> 23:54.900
会在哪儿?
And where would that be?

23:54.910 --> 23:59.940
不只是地点还有时间
It's not just the where but the when.

23:59.950 --> 24:04.140
而且时间就快到了
That when is coming up soon.

24:04.150 --> 24:08.810
但我想先谈谈条件
But I want to cut a deal first.

24:09.910 --> 24:12.280
给我点时间
Give us a minute.

24:22.170 --> 24:23.870
你还有什么想说的？
Anything you want to say?

24:26.050 --> 24:27.660
一天
One day.

24:28.920 --> 24:31.570
我们只有这些了
That's all we had.

24:54.950 --> 24:58.400
在那几天里
Back then,

24:58.410 --> 25:00.140
情况最惨的时候...
when things were at their worst...

25:00.150 --> 25:02.000
有那么几天我以为
there were days I thought

25:02.010 --> 25:05.040
我再也见不到阳光了
I'd never see the sun again.

25:05.050 --> 25:10.150
但他救了我一命
But he saved my life.

25:11.080 --> 25:16.750
我只希望他能把我们当作他生活的一部分
I just wish he could have let us be a part of his.

25:19.880 --> 25:23.280
是啊
Yeah.

25:30.550 --> 25:35.450
我会告诉他的  好的
I'll tell him.

25:37.280 --> 25:39.140
这是开给你的条件
Here's the deal.

25:39.150 --> 25:40.970
所有指控都被撤消并且政府
All charges dropped and the government

25:40.980 --> 25:43.840
会负责你的医疗费用直到你被驱逐出境
picks up medical costs until you're fit to be deported,

25:43.850 --> 25:48.170
只要你提供正确的信息
all contingent upon your information being accurate.

25:48.180 --> 25:50.400
斯科菲尔德在哪儿?
Where's Scofield?

25:50.410 --> 25:52.940
不要驱逐出境
No deportation.

25:52.950 --> 25:54.700
我要美国公民身份
I want citizenship.

25:54.710 --> 25:58.070
公民身份?
Citizenship?

25:58.080 --> 26:02.780
做为和你们合作的动机  而且我要书面的
A little incentive, and I want it in writing.

26:02.910 --> 26:04.470
我不想再和你玩下去了
I'm so tired of playing games.

26:04.480 --> 26:08.980
那么开始打字吧
Well, start typing.

26:12.510 --> 26:16.500
没有外接起博器
No external pacemaker.

26:16.510 --> 26:20.270
这个不错...没有吗啡滴液
Oh, this is a good one-- no morphine drip.

26:20.280 --> 26:22.040
-你在做什么?  -FBI 出去出去
What are you doing? FBI. Out. Out!

26:22.050 --> 26:23.040
出去出去！
Out. Out!

26:23.050 --> 26:25.200
你他妈做什么?
What the hell are you doing?

26:25.210 --> 26:27.640
给你点合作的动机啊
Giving you a little incentive.

26:27.650 --> 26:29.440
别!
Come on!

26:29.450 --> 26:30.640
别这样  你个狗娘...
Come on, you son of A...

26:30.650 --> 26:32.670
他们什么也没找到?
And they found nothing?

26:32.680 --> 26:35.370
好的谢了
Okay, thanks.

26:35.380 --> 26:37.340
你的直觉真强啊  布拉德
Well, your instincts are great, Brad,

26:37.350 --> 26:40.170
管区警察今天是派了人到郝兰德的家里去了
but the precinct actually sent a unit over to Hollander's house today.

26:40.180 --> 26:41.970
一个匿名报警电话声称有人闯入
An anonymous caller said they saw an intruder

26:41.980 --> 26:43.340
但里面没人
but no one was there.

26:43.350 --> 26:45.140
该死的
Damn it.

26:45.150 --> 26:47.040
如果你知道博格威尔和郝兰德的事
If you knew about Bagwell and Hollander,

26:47.050 --> 26:50.070
为什么你们不到那里去(找他)呢?
why didn't you just head over there yourself?

26:50.080 --> 26:52.800
我们找不到那地方
We couldn't find the house.

26:52.810 --> 26:54.600
是吗?
Really?

26:54.610 --> 26:58.310
电话簿里有啊
It's listed.

27:01.380 --> 27:06.210
失陪一下
excuse me.

27:11.050 --> 27:13.870
谢谢
Thank you.

27:13.880 --> 27:16.440
一切都好吗?
Everything okay?

27:16.450 --> 27:20.800
是啊一切都好
Yeah, yeah, everything's fine.

27:20.810 --> 27:23.240
布拉德  你曾经去过冯特洛利酒店吗?
Brad, have you ever been to the Fauntleroy hotel?

27:23.250 --> 27:25.340
-大概离这里15分钟的路 -从来没听说过
It's about 15 minutes from here.-Never heard of it.

27:25.350 --> 27:28.070
那就奇怪了  他们找到
Well, that's strange,'cause they found

27:28.080 --> 27:31.270
这张收据  就在盖伊的房间里
this receipt in Geary's hotel room.

27:31.280 --> 27:34.580
是用你的信用卡结的
It's from your credit card.

27:35.550 --> 27:39.710
我不知道怎么会跑那里去的
I don't know how that got there.

27:43.110 --> 27:46.000
我觉得你是在回避这个问题
I think you're being evasive.

27:46.010 --> 27:47.940
你应该跟我说实话  贝利克先生
You should tell me the truth, Mr.Bellick.

27:47.950 --> 27:51.240
怎么不叫我布拉德了?
What happened to "Brad"?

27:51.250 --> 27:53.370
大概7年前我办了第一起
About seven years ago, I got my first

27:53.380 --> 27:54.900
凶杀案--一个漂亮的女子
homicide case   a woman, pretty.

27:54.910 --> 27:56.100
被粗暴的袭击
She was brutally attacked.

27:56.110 --> 27:58.270
她那兽性的男友留着她等死
Animal boyfriend left her for dead,

27:58.280 --> 28:00.700
但她还有口气...勉强的
but she was still breathing... barely.

28:00.710 --> 28:03.900
她在她的手机上输入了
But she punched into her cell phone

28:03.910 --> 28:07.470
凶手的号码  结果她就帮我们破了案
the killer's number,so she solved the crime for us.

28:07.480 --> 28:09.770
当我们找到那收据的时候  布拉德
When we found the receipt, Brad,

28:09.780 --> 28:12.670
盖瑞的手  他的手指着你的名字
it was in Geary's hand, his finger pointing to your name.

28:12.680 --> 28:14.970
他用生前最后一点力气告诉我们你杀了他
With his last ounce of strength, he told us you killed him.

28:14.980 --> 28:16.270
好吧  听着
Okay, listen.

28:16.280 --> 28:19.000
盖瑞和我在郝兰德家里发现了博格威尔
Geary and I found Bagwell at Hollander's house.

28:19.010 --> 28:20.340
我们逼问了他
We roughed him up

28:20.350 --> 28:22.500
直到他告诉我们
till he told us

28:22.510 --> 28:24.800
他从犹它挖来的那500万的下落
here he'd hid the five million bucks we knew he dug up in utah.

28:24.810 --> 28:27.140
等我们找到那笔钱后格雷耍了我
When we found the money,Geary double-crossed me.

28:27.150 --> 28:29.470
他把我打晕并拿走了钱
He hit me in the head and took the cash.

28:29.480 --> 28:31.140
我和格雷的死没关系
I had nothing to do with Geary's death.

28:31.150 --> 28:32.270
你听见我说的了吗?
You hear what I'm saying?

